  "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/questions/2274102/difference-between-using-throwable-and-exception-in-a-try-catch",
  "closed_reason" : "Duplicate",
  "title" : "Difference between using Throwable and Exception in a try catch",
  "body" : "<p>Sometimes, I see</p>\n\n<pre><code>try {\n\n} catch(Throwable e) {\n\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>And sometimes</p>\n\n<pre><code>try {\n\n} catch(Exception e) {\n\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>What is the difference?</p>\n"
